limit.description: Maximum number of items which may be returned.

since.description: Timestamp to only include items created since then.

until.description: Timestamp to only include items created until then.

types.description: Comma-delimited list of event \"types\" to filter the results by.

userId.description: Deprecated. Use `principalId` instead. If `principalId` and `userId` both exist, `principalId` will be used.

principalId.description: When retrieving events for a Team, the `principalId` parameter may be specified to filter events generated by a specific principal.

withPayload.description: When set to `true`, the response will include the `payload` field for each event.

teamId.description: The Team identifier to perform the request on behalf of.

slug.description: The Team slug to perform the request on behalf of.
